text:
Facebook will ban all political ads after the polls close in the U.S. on Nov. 3, indefinitely. 

The company plans to place notifications at the top of the News Feed notifying people that no winner had been decided until one was declared by news outlets. https://t.co/E5DmgJ7IoZ
